description: Waiting for a new appointment with Volto Nascosto for the fate of his friend Vittorio, Hugo stops at a block of the Italian garrison, where the war wounded are admitted. The commander of the outpost is slave of a jealousy obsession for his ethiopian concubine. In his view, Ugo has made ​​an impression on her, and is therefore a dangerous rival to eliminate.
name: Il presidio

description: Ugo, reached Addis Ababa where the Italian war prisoners are kept, fails to find Vittorio, who seems imprisoned elsewhere being probably the subject of negotiation between political and military echelons. Therefore he tries to enter this intricate network of relationships and secrets, regardless of risk, while Queen Taytu seems to adjust the events with an occult direction ...
name: Il prigioniero di Menelik

description: Ugo has finally managed to secure the release of Vittorio. Volto Nascosto is long gone, vanished like a mirage in the desert. But on the ship that brings the two friends at home, the ghost of the masked raider returns to materialize: it is only the manifestation of an obsession, or the mystery that still surrounds his figure is about to expand and raise alarms in Italy as well?
name: La liberazione

description: Back in Rome, Vittorio is celebrated as a hero. He has no intention to see Matilde again, admitted to a psychiatric asylum. She no longer trusts the return of her lover, believing him dead. She seem to have accepted the death and his health seems to have benefited. Ugo can't decide what to do: to tell her that Vittorio is back in Rome or to leave her unaware?
name: Medaglia d'oro

description: Vittorio is about to receive the Gold Medal. Matilde, who fled from the psychiatric clinic where she is hospitalized, runs to him. But Vittorio rejects her, and Ugo fears that the disappointment will again undermine her health. Will he save her? Africa is now far away, but Volto Nascosto, or maybe his spectrum, seems still chasing the two friends. All nodes are coming home to roost, and Volto Nascosto is now ready to drop the mask
name: Dietro la maschera

description: Allen the Alien returns to Earth as directed by the Coalition of Planets - he's come to gather information from Mark about his father - the Viltrumite Traitor. Meanwhile, the Viltrumites have come to Earth to check up on Mark's progress as the reluctant Viltrumite Agent of Earth.
name: Volume Nine

description:
Leaving behind East Africa and all its misfortunes, Ugo Pastore arrives in Shanghai in 1897 to help his father Enea, salesman of the Caput Mundi trading company.

Unable to endure the injustices, He quickly realizes that the Western powers keep harassing the local population. He tighten friendship with Ha Ojie, a young actor of a notable acting company, who one day accompanies Ugo at the whorehouse of Madame Niang. There he meets Meifong, a novice prostitute but with a gentile soul, which he immediately fall in love. Ugo path will clash with that of Lord Burke, an English trafficker who, like many others at that time, ran an illegal trade of opium.

When Burke attack Meifong, Ugo decides to make him pay, wearing once again the silver mask.

A new masked avenger watches over the city streets, a figure that the British press wastes no time to identify with the name of : The Shanghai Devil.
name: Il trafficante d'oppio

description: The great Aral sea, once a huge inland sea rich in fish and with luxuriant vegetation growing all around its shores, has been reduced to a stagnant swamp by the reckless hand of man. It is now strewn with the rusting hulks of ships stranded in the dirt and the remains of wharfs, quays and docks. But death makes its presence felt not only through the effects of this ecological catastrophe that Arno and Rena, members of the “Medical Team”, are trying to fight against with every means at their disposal. For there is a lethal menace on the loose in the desert: Erlik Khan, and not even Harlan, Tesla and Kurjak are able to undertake any action against him; it’s a threat that goes hand in hand with the horror that dwells on the island abandoned in the middle of the Aral Sea...
name: Il mare della morte

description: Switzerland is proverbially a quiet and idyllic land, rich in snowy peaks and green pastures. But for Harlan Draka it opens up the doors of horror, when he discovers that the serial killer Rudolph Scholberg, aka “the Cannibal”, is only one of the numerous followers of Thorke, the legendary demon that has plagued mankind since the dawn of time. And this is not all: during this Swiss interlude, we also get to make the acquaintance of the award-winning canned meat factory Blumenstock…
name: Gli insaziabili

description: The Snaefellsjökull is considered by many to be a sacred place, a rocky outcrop that preserves mysterious powers in its remotest underground passages and recesses, including that of awakening the dead from their slumbers. In the wake of a series of inexplicable disappearances that have occurred on the desolate plains of the Island of Ice, Harlan and Kurjak come up against the enigma of the Snaefellsjökull, a criminal wielding an axe who believes he is possessed by Odin but who actually reincarnates the spirit of a blood-thirsty sixteenth-century murderer, and the legend contained in an ancient saga that narrates the deeds of two indomitable Viking warriors, exterminators of trolls and bersekers…
name: Sotto il vulcano

description: The ancient cult of Odin blends with the New Age fantasies of a community of Americans who have settled in Iceland; meanwhile Harland and Kurjak, guided towards the unknowable by the psychic Gudrun, are trying to unravel the mystery of the many, oh far too many disappearances that have occurred on the slopes of the Snaefellsjökull, the volcano described by ancient tradition as opening that leads to the center of the Earth… But the answer to the questions is to be found in the Ice King’s Grotto, in the very place where the Viking heroes Egil- the Una-Mano and Asmund the Fierce killed the king of the Trolls…
name: La caverna dei Troll

description: The Shade's quest to find out who ordered his assassination takes him to Barcelona, where he stumbles upon a decades-old feud between a teenaged vampire and her archenemy. What does this feud have to do with the Shade's origin? A crucial piece of the puzzle is revealed here!
name: Memoria Roja

description: Sinister Haversham Priory is the most haunted house in the whole of England - from the Infernal Hounds prowling around outside to the faceless Monk of the crypt, from the Lady dressed in gray who wanders through the attic to the gruesome “elemental” spirit that lurks in the portrait gallery… Well, I mean, it could very well be considered as the most exhaustive category that’s ever existed as far as ghostly apparitions are concerned! The University of York sends out a very experienced team of ghost hunters, all of them shining examples of the fighting spirit, headed by Professor Halloway and the spiritist Maud Nightingale. They’re specialists, used to the worst, but nothing they have faced so far could possibly have prepared them for the horror that awaits them within the walls of Haversham. Luckily, an ally of no mean stature stands by their side: Harlan Draka!
name: I cacciatori di fantasmi

description: The fight against the telepathic mutants led by Aran Darko breaks out. New efforts and new sacrifices are required from Alfa agents and their allies, for what could be the last battle. Sigmund Baginov and Link, helped by the technopaths, think they have finally found a way to get the victory. All are ready ... will they really succeed in putting an end to the attempt to conquer Earth by the army under the command of Kos Aradan I, Emperor of Mars?
name: Scontro finale

description:
Because you asked for it - Spider-Man in Spaaaace! Trapped 22,300 miles above the Earth, Spidey has to rescue John Jameson from the ongoing machinations of Doctor Octopus! Plus: a guest star so special and so secret we can't even tell you until next issue!

The issue starts with John Jameson out in space aboard the Apogee-1, Horizons Space Shuttle, Jameson is talking to his had and having a conversation when suddenly the feed goes off. Jonah starts panicking and the Horizon team tries to check on the vitals on the station as Peter leaves and Suits up into Spider-man, he goes to the Baxter Building to get help. After a conversation with Johnny Storm, Johnny agrees to come and they go on the FF's Rocket Ship. Making it up, they enter the station, to soon be attacked by a swarm of octobots, but John Jameson comes and saves them, telling them to come with him.

Meanwhile, in the underwater base of the Sinister Six, Doctor Octupus's condition has worsened and he discusses the plan, saying they only need twenty minutes to complete their mission then bomb the Apogee-1, Meanwhile, the three heroes soon discover the crew is being controlled by Octobots and turned into Zombie-like, and they are coming after them.
name: The Galaxy's Greatest Super-Hero. Part One

description: Up until this point, Invincible has been working for the Global Defense agency. Fighting their fights, defeating their enemies... now something's not right, Invincible can no longer carry out his orders unquestioned. Now he finds himself up against the very organization he's been working for!
name: Volume Ten

description: The Justice League is united at last against Darkseid! The awesome consequences of this high-stakes battle will resonate within the series for years to come! Geoff Johns and Jim Lee end their historic first arc with a bang!
name: Justice League, Part Six; Pandora
